data.description: What a Find!  Come see this Absolutely FANTASTIC Rancher in Aspen Hill with no HOA fees!  So many UPDATES have been done for you already!  The MAIN BATHROOM has been UPDATED so Perfectly that it belongs in a magazine, and it is HUGE...from its Standalone CLAWFOOT TUB to the Glass STAND-UP Shower and from the Black and White Color Contrasts to the Clean look of the Chrome Fixtures!  The HEATLAMP is ready to do it's job.  The Kitchen has been RENOVATED with a Modern Look and Feel, while the Dining Area has some EXTRA Cabinetry and a Built-in DESK SPACE.  There is a Separate LAUNDRY ROOM where you will find a Washer/Dryer and some EXTRA STORAGE SPACE.  Off to the other side of the Home is the MASTER BEDROOM with its Newly Added WALK-IN CLOSET, and I assure you it is BIG enough for two!  There is a BONUS ROOM off the Kitchen towards the back of the home, which opens to your OWN BACKYARD OASIS.  High FENCING in the Backyard allows for your Privacy, while Extensive HARDSCAPING which looks AMAZING has been completed.  Out Back you have your own PATIO, GRILL, and POND!  A GREENHOUSE SHED has been built with RECLAIMED MATERIALS, and it is waiting for your Seedlings.  The ROOF has been Done Recently, as many other UPGRADES within the last 3 years.   A MUST SEE!  Grab your Agent...and tell them to Grab a Blank CONTRACT!
